After hearing the plenipotentiary of the Wetthaus at 3.50 p.m., Larrazabal Bretón was immediately released.
The court secretary, Jorge Yánez, went to the San Nicolás de los Garza City Prison to inform Jonás that he had been acquitted and that his case was filed.
